Travis Tedford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Travis_Tedford 0 Travis William Tedford (born August 19, 1988) is an American former actor. A child actor during the 1990s, he is best known for portraying Our Gang kid Spanky McFarland in the 1994 feature film The Little Rascals and for being the first Welch's "advertising-spokeskid" beginning in 1994 at age 5.
